00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.000
What does calculate the spread is called the variance.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:31.000
Now we will compute the variance of the data, and the very first trick you apply is,

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:37.000
we normalized these sequences by subtracting the mean from each data item.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:45.000
So in the case of the friends, if we subtract 18 from 17 we get -1, 1, 0, -1, 1.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:53.000
